QuestData.Title: Something Foul is Afoot
QuestData.Description: You notice a stronger-than-usual smell permeating from ahead. Your stomach lurches as the thick smell fills your nostrils.$b $bYou recognize this smell, it's saurok. Rotting, discarded saurok flesh infused with the foul waste of the sewer.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Flesh'rok gurgles and moans in the distance.
QuestData.LogDescription: Seek and destroy Flesh'rok the Diseased.
